Constrict	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SalamanderSubRaceTrait.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A salamander deals automatic tail slap damage (including fire damage) with a successful grapple check. A noble salamander can constrict multiple creatures simultaneously, provided they are all at least two sizes smaller than it.	KEY:Salamander ~ Constrict																											SOURCEPAGE:MM1	
