Improved Grab	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SalamanderSubRaceTrait.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.Improved Grab	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:To use this ability, a salamander must hit a creature of up to one size larger than itself with its tail slap attack. It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity. If it wins the grapple check, it establishes a hold and can constrict.	KEY:Salamander ~ Improved Grab																											SOURCEPAGE:MM1	
